item.title: Please Read and Send FeedBack
item.dc:creator: @Dblocknc005 Dblocknc005
item.description:
@Dblocknc005 wrote:

i need one on one problem solving from some people that have active running servers i am having some connecting to server issues in my client and some coding questions and a few other bugs and kinks that i’m having trouble working out if anyone can help please please email me I could use as much input as possible the reason i am asking for one on one help is because i have posted 11 or so posts on this forum and no one has given me any helpful feedback and i’m getting irritated with it so if anyone would like to truly help a member in need please let me know… I am looking for general help and experienced coding techs to help work out my issues i am computer literate but am new to the java world and am learning as i go so i’m having the usual newbie problems and just need some positive guidance… Thanks to all that are willing to help…

Sincerely,
Darren
